    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a solid daily driver. While it is mechanically sound and runs smoothly, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dings on the passenger side, and some fading in the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows typical wear and tear from regular use. It\u2019s a practical choice for a buyer who prioritizes functional performance over a perfect cosmetic appearance.",
