    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels brand new. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
