    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of Zuffenhausen engineering. Featuring the iconic widebody silhouette and a naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six, this unit boasts a pin-straight chassis and a factory-spec M96 powerplant with a documented IMS bearing retrofit. The Getrag-sourced six-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, while the viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system ensures optimal torque distribution. Suspension geometry remains perfectly indexed, providing telepathic feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Finished in flawless paint with zero oxidation on the undercarriage, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
